63 void MotionPlanningFrame::saveSceneButtonClicked()
64 {
65  if (planning_scene_storage_)
66  {
67  const std::string& name = planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRO()->getName();
68  if (name.empty() || planning_scene_storage_->hasPlanningScene(name))
69  {
70  std::unique_ptr<QMessageBox> q;
71  if (name.empty())
72  q = std::make_unique<QMessageBox>(
73  QMessageBox::Question, "Change Planning Scene Name",
74  QString("The name for the planning scene should not be empty. Would you like to rename "
75  "the planning scene?'"),
76  QMessageBox::Cancel, this);
77  else
78  q = std::make_unique<QMessageBox>(QMessageBox::Question, "Confirm Planning Scene Overwrite",
79  QString("A planning scene named '")
80  .append(name.c_str())
81  .append("' already exists. Do you wish to "
82  "overwrite that scene?"),
83  QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No, this);
84  std::unique_ptr<QPushButton> rename(q->addButton("&Rename", QMessageBox::AcceptRole));
85  if (q->exec() != QMessageBox::Yes)
86  {
87  if (q->clickedButton() == rename.get())
88  {
89  bool ok = false;
90  QString new_name = QInputDialog::getText(this, "Rename Planning Scene",
91  "New name for the planning scene:", QLineEdit::Normal,
92  QString::fromStdString(name), &ok);
93  if (ok)
94  {
95  planning_display_->getPlanningSceneRW()->setName(new_name.toStdString());
96  rviz::Property* prop = planning_display_->subProp("Scene Geometry")->subProp("Scene Name");
97  if (prop)
98  {
99  bool old = prop->blockSignals(true);
100  prop->setValue(new_name);
101  prop->blockSignals(old);
102  }
103  saveSceneButtonClicked();
104  }
105  return;
106  }
107  return;
108  }
109  }
110 
111  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeSaveSceneButtonClicked, this),
112  "save scene");
113  }
114 }

121 void MotionPlanningFrame::saveQueryButtonClicked()
122 {
123  if (planning_scene_storage_)
124  {
125  QList<QTreeWidgetItem*> sel = ui_->planning_scene_tree->selectedItems();
126  if (!sel.empty())
127  {
128  QTreeWidgetItem* s = sel.front();
129 
130  // if we have selected a PlanningScene, add the query as a new one, under that planning scene
131  if (s->type() == ITEM_TYPE_SCENE)
132  {
133  std::string scene = s->text(0).toStdString();
134  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(
135  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeSaveQueryButtonClicked, this, scene, ""), "save query");
136  }
137  else
138  {
139  // if we selected a query name, then we overwrite that query
140  std::string scene = s->parent()->text(0).toStdString();
141  std::string query_name = s->text(0).toStdString();
142 
143  while (query_name.empty() || planning_scene_storage_->hasPlanningQuery(scene, query_name))
144  {
145  std::unique_ptr<QMessageBox> q;
146  if (query_name.empty())
147  q = std::make_unique<QMessageBox>(
148  QMessageBox::Question, "Change Planning Query Name",
149  QString("The name for the planning query should not be empty. Would you like to "
150  "rename the planning query?'"),
151  QMessageBox::Cancel, this);
152  else
153  q = std::make_unique<QMessageBox>(QMessageBox::Question, "Confirm Planning Query Overwrite",
154  QString("A planning query named '")
155  .append(query_name.c_str())
156  .append("' already exists. Do you wish "
157  "to overwrite that query?"),
158  QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No, this);
159  std::unique_ptr<QPushButton> rename(q->addButton("&Rename", QMessageBox::AcceptRole));
160  if (q->exec() == QMessageBox::Yes)
161  break;
162  else
163  {
164  if (q->clickedButton() == rename.get())
165  {
166  bool ok = false;
167  QString new_name = QInputDialog::getText(this, "Rename Planning Query",
168  "New name for the planning query:", QLineEdit::Normal,
169  QString::fromStdString(query_name), &ok);
170  if (ok)
171  query_name = new_name.toStdString();
172  else
173  return;
174  }
175  else
176  return;
177  }
178  }
179  planning_display_->addBackgroundJob(
180  boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::computeSaveQueryButtonClicked, this, scene, query_name), "save query");
181  }
182  }
183  }
184 }

210 void MotionPlanningFrame::warehouseItemNameChanged(QTreeWidgetItem* item, int column)
211 {
212  if (item->text(column) == item->toolTip(column) || item->toolTip(column).length() == 0)
213  return;
214  moveit_warehouse::PlanningSceneStoragePtr planning_scene_storage = planning_scene_storage_;
215  if (!planning_scene_storage)
216  return;
217 
218  if (item->type() == ITEM_TYPE_SCENE)
219  {
220  std::string new_name = item->text(column).toStdString();
221 
222  if (planning_scene_storage->hasPlanningScene(new_name))
223  {
224  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populatePlanningSceneTreeView, this));
225  QMessageBox::warning(this, "Scene not renamed",
226  QString("The scene name '").append(item->text(column)).append("' already exists"));
227  return;
228  }
229  else
230  {
231  std::string old_name = item->toolTip(column).toStdString();
232  planning_scene_storage->renamePlanningScene(old_name, new_name);
233  item->setToolTip(column, item->text(column));
234  }
235  }
236  else
237  {
238  std::string scene = item->parent()->text(0).toStdString();
239  std::string new_name = item->text(column).toStdString();
240  if (planning_scene_storage->hasPlanningQuery(scene, new_name))
241  {
242  planning_display_->addMainLoopJob(boost::bind(&MotionPlanningFrame::populatePlanningSceneTreeView, this));
243  QMessageBox::warning(this, "Query not renamed",
244  QString("The query name '")
245  .append(item->text(column))
246  .append("' already exists for scene ")
247  .append(item->parent()->text(0)));
248  return;
249  }
250  else
251  {
252  std::string old_name = item->toolTip(column).toStdString();
253  planning_scene_storage->renamePlanningQuery(scene, old_name, new_name);
254  item->setToolTip(column, item->text(column));
255  }
256  }
257 }

259 void MotionPlanningFrame::populatePlanningSceneTreeView()
260 {
261  moveit_warehouse::PlanningSceneStoragePtr planning_scene_storage = planning_scene_storage_;
262  if (!planning_scene_storage)
263  return;
264 
265  ui_->planning_scene_tree->setUpdatesEnabled(false);
266 
267  // remember which items were expanded
268  std::set<std::string> expanded;
269  for (int i = 0; i < ui_->planning_scene_tree->topLevelItemCount(); ++i)
270  {
271  QTreeWidgetItem* it = ui_->planning_scene_tree->topLevelItem(i);
272  if (it->isExpanded())
273  expanded.insert(it->text(0).toStdString());
274  }
275 
276  ui_->planning_scene_tree->clear();
277  std::vector<std::string> names;
278  planning_scene_storage->getPlanningSceneNames(names);
279 
280  for (const std::string& name : names)
281  {
282  std::vector<std::string> query_names;
283  planning_scene_storage->getPlanningQueriesNames(query_names, name);
284  QTreeWidgetItem* item =
285  new QTreeWidgetItem(ui_->planning_scene_tree, QStringList(QString::fromStdString(name)), ITEM_TYPE_SCENE);
286  item->setFlags(item->flags() | Qt::ItemIsEditable);
287  item->setToolTip(0, item->text(0)); // we use the tool tip as a backup of the old name when renaming
288  for (const std::string& query_name : query_names)
289  {
290  QTreeWidgetItem* subitem =
291  new QTreeWidgetItem(item, QStringList(QString::fromStdString(query_name)), ITEM_TYPE_QUERY);
292  subitem->setFlags(subitem->flags() | Qt::ItemIsEditable);
293  subitem->setToolTip(0, subitem->text(0));
294  item->addChild(subitem);
295  }
296 
297  ui_->planning_scene_tree->insertTopLevelItem(ui_->planning_scene_tree->topLevelItemCount(), item);
298  if (expanded.find(name) != expanded.end())
299  ui_->planning_scene_tree->expandItem(item);
300  }
301  ui_->planning_scene_tree->sortItems(0, Qt::AscendingOrder);
302  ui_->planning_scene_tree->setUpdatesEnabled(true);
303  checkPlanningSceneTreeEnabledButtons();
304 }
